column5: Anyone heading to Halley's Camp (Caribou Falls) on or around June 7th to June 13th? Our normal crew of idiots are headed up again this year... I think its my 12th year! RV's and boats, stop by and have a beer if you are up there. Any fishing report would be appreciated! Canadian Countdown 2009 @ http://www.walleyecrazy.com
What kind of beer you have Erik?
It depends if the LCBO is open when we go through Rainy River... Labatts and Bohemian are the two I enjoy.
I will stop over this year.Last year I didn't get the post till after we left.We will be up there June 6th-12th..See ya there Erik!!
